{
  "doc_id": "58743",
  "text": "IRIDA provides fast genome distance calculation through the RefSeqMasher pipeline (github.com/phac-nml/refseq_masher), which uses Mash (Mash v2.0+) [CITATION_1] and a k-mer based Mash sketch database of 54,925 NCBI RefSeq genomes to enable users to quickly match the submitted isolate reads to the closest matching reference genomes. The RefSeq Masher pipeline can be used to select appropriate reference genomes for use with SNVPhyl or to identify possible contamination. In IRIDA, RefSeqMasher results are presented in tabular form, sorted by the closest matching genome.",
