      "citation_id": "[CITATION_1]",
      "span_text": "IRIDA provides fast genome distance calculation through the RefSeqMasher pipeline (github.com/phac-nml/refseq_masher), which uses Mash (Mash v2.0+) and a k-mer based Mash sketch database of 54,925 NCBI RefSeq genomes to enable users to quickly match the submitted isolate reads to the closest matching reference genomes."
